message.en_US: Human...
message.pt_BR: Humana...
message.de_DE: Mensch...

message.en_US: Thank you again for bringing peace to our village.
message.pt_BR: Mais uma vez agradeço por trazer paz à nossa aldeia
message.de_DE: Danke nochmals für bringen Frieden in unser Dorf.
message.zh_CN: 感谢你为我们村庄带来了和平。<<A<<[CHANGED 2017/12/12]
message.ko_KR: 우리 마을에 평화를 가져다주어 다시 한번 고맙군요...<<A<<[CHANGED 2017/11/16]
message.ja_JP:
我らの村に平和を
もたらしてくれて、
重ね重ねありがとう。<<A<<[CHANGED 2017/11/27]
message.zh_TW: 感謝你為我們村莊帶來了和平。<<A<<[CHANGED 2017/12/12]

message.en_US: Human \v[lore.title.seeker]...
message.pt_BR: \v[lore.title.seeker] Humana...
message.de_DE: Seeker-Mensch...
message.zh_CN: 人类\v[lore.title.seeker]...<<A<<[CHANGED 2020/07/08]
message.ja_JP: 人間の\v[lore.title.seeker]よ...<<A<<[CHANGED 2020/07/03]

message.en_US: Hi!\. Meet!\. Lea!
message.pt_BR: Oi!\. Encontrar!\. Lea!
message.de_DE: Hi!\. Treffen!\. Lea!

message.en_US: Human want bring human machine into village?
message.pt_BR: Os humanos querem trazer a máquina deles para a aldeia?
message.de_DE: Mensch will bringen Menschmaschine in Dorf?
message.zh_CN: 人类想把人类机器带到村子里？<<A<<[CHANGED 2020/07/08]
message.zh_TW: 感謝你為我們村莊帶來了和平。<<A<<[CHANGED 2020/07/09]
message.ja_JP: 人間、人間のマシン、村に持ち込みたいか？<<A<<[CHANGED 2020/07/03]
message.ko_KR: 인간 기계를 우리 마을에 들이고 싶나, 인간?<<A<<[CHANGED 2020/07/08]

message.en_US: [nods]
message.pt_BR: [acena a cabeça]
message.de_DE: [nickt]
message.ja_JP: [うなずく]<<A<<[CHANGED 2020/07/03]

message.en_US: \v[lore.title.seeker], we thankful for your help and peace with human is big boon for shad.
message.pt_BR: \v[lore.title.seeker], agradecemos por sua ajuda. A paz com o seres humanos é uma grande bênção para os shad.
message.de_DE: Seeker, wir dankbar für deine Hilfe und Friede mit Mensch ist großer Segen für Shad.
message.zh_CN: \v[lore.title.seeker]，感谢你的帮助，和人类的和平为沙德带来了繁荣。<<A<<[CHANGED 2020/07/08]
message.zh_TW: 感謝你為我們村莊帶來了和平。<<A<<[CHANGED 2020/07/09]
message.ja_JP:
\v[lore.title.seeker]さん、あなたの助け、
感謝する。
人間と平和にできる、これ、
シャッドに大きな恵み。<<A<<[CHANGED 2020/07/03]
message.ko_KR: \v[lore.title.seeker], 인간의 도움 고맙게 생각한다. 인간과의 평화는 샤드에게 큰 혜택이다.<<A<<[CHANGED 2020/07/08]

message.en_US: However,\. human machines full of dirt and hunger for fuel.\. This can not become part of shad life.
message.pt_BR: No entanto, as máquinas dos humanos são cheias de sujeira e fome de combustível. Isto não pode se tornar parte da vida dos shad.
message.de_DE: Doch Menschmaschine voller Dreck und Hunger nach Energie.\. Für Shadleben nicht vereinbar.
message.zh_CN: 但是，\.人类机器污染，贪吃燃料。\.这不能成为沙德生活的一部分。<<A<<[CHANGED 2020/07/08]
message.zh_TW: 感謝你為我們村莊帶來了和平。<<A<<[CHANGED 2020/07/09]
message.ja_JP:
しかし、\.人間のマシン、汚くて
いつも燃料に飢えている。
\.シャッドの生活の一部にはなれない。<<A<<[CHANGED 2020/07/03]
message.ko_KR: 하지만,\. 인간 기계 더럽고 연료가 필요하다.\. 샤드 삶의 일부가 될 수 없다.<<A<<[CHANGED 2020/07/08]

message.en_US: Unless using them in clean way can be found I will no give my blessing.
message.pt_BR: A menos que seja possível encontrar uma máquina que funcione de forma limpa, não darei minha bênção.
message.de_DE: Wenn kein Weg finden, Maschine laufen auf sauber Art, ich nicht geben meinen Segen.
message.zh_CN: 除非能有清洁的能源，否则我不会同意使用电力。<<A<<[CHANGED 2020/07/08]
message.zh_TW: 感謝你為我們村莊帶來了和平。<<A<<[CHANGED 2020/07/09]
message.ja_JP:
清潔に使える方法、見つからねば、
皆に恵みを与えられない。<<A<<[CHANGED 2020/07/03]
message.ko_KR: 깨끗하게 사용할 방법 없으면 허락할 수 없다.<<A<<[CHANGED 2020/07/08]

message.en_US: \v[lore.title.seeker] best take walk through Shad village and talk with people if still desire to find way to unify machine with our ways.
message.pt_BR: \v[lore.title.seeker] é melhor andar pela aldeia e conversar com os Shad, se ainda deseja encontrar uma forma ideal de incluir as máquinas na nossa cultura.
message.de_DE: Seeker gehen am besten durch Shaddorf und sprechen mit Shad, ob sie Weg finden möchten, Maschine mit Shadleben zu vereinen.<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/05/22]
message.zh_CN: \v[lore.title.seeker]，你如果想要让机器融入沙德的生活，请在我们的村里走一走，和大家谈一谈吧。<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/05/22]
message.zh_TW: 感謝你為我們村莊帶來了和平。<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/05/22]
message.ja_JP:
\v[lore.title.seeker]さん、シャッドの村を
歩いて、今もマシンを我らのものと
したいか聞いてみてくだされ。<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/05/22]
message.ko_KR: \v[lore.title.seeker], 기계를 들일 방법을 찾고 싶다면 샤드 마을 돌아다니며 주민들에게 말을 걸어봐라.<<A<<[CHANGED 2020/07/08]

message.en_US: Lea.\. Meet.\. Bye.
message.pt_BR: Lea.\. Encontrar.\. Tchau.
message.de_DE: Lea.\. Treffen.\. Bye.
message.ja_JP: レア。\.会おう。\.じゃあね。<<A<<[CHANGED 2020/07/03]

message.en_US: Human machines full of dirt and hunger for fuel.\. This can not become part of shad life.
message.pt_BR: As máquinas dos humanos são cheias de sujeira e fome de combustível. Isto não pode se tornar parte da vida dos shad.
message.de_DE: Menschmaschine voller Dreck und Hunger nach Energie.\. Für Shadleben nicht vereinbar.
message.zh_CN: 人类机器全是泥土，渴望燃料。\.这不能成为沙德的生活。<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/01/12]
message.zh_TW: 感謝你為我們村莊帶來了和平。<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/01/12]
message.ja_JP:
人間のマシン、汚くて
いつも燃料に飢えている。
\.シャッドの生活の一部にはなれない。<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/01/12]
message.ko_KR: 인간 기계 더럽고 연료가 필요하다.\. 샤드 삶의 일부가 될 수 없다.<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/01/12]

message.en_US: Unless using them in clean way can be found I will not give my blessing.
message.pt_BR: A menos que seja possível usá-las de forma limpa, não darei minha bênção.
message.de_DE: Wenn kein Weg finden, Maschine laufen auf sauber Art, ich nicht geben meinen Segen.
message.zh_CN: 除非能有清洁的能源，否则我不会同意使用电力。<<A<<[CHANGED 2020/07/08]
message.zh_TW: 感謝你為我們村莊帶來了和平。<<A<<[CHANGED 2020/07/09]
message.ja_JP:
清潔に使える方法、見つからねば、
皆に恵みを与えられない。<<A<<[CHANGED 2020/07/03]
message.ko_KR: 깨끗하게 사용할 방법 없으면 허락할 수 없다.<<A<<[CHANGED 2020/07/08]

message.en_US: \v[lore.title.seeker] best take walk through shad village and talk with people if still desire to find way to unify machine with our ways.
message.pt_BR: \v[lore.title.seeker] é melhor andar pela aldeia e conversar com os Shad, se ainda deseja encontrar uma forma ideal de incluir as máquinas na nossa cultura.
message.de_DE: Seeker gehen am besten durch Shaddorf und sprechen mit Shad, ob sie Weg finden möchten, Maschine mit Shadleben zu vereinen.
message.zh_CN: \v[lore.title.seeker]，你如果想要让机器融入沙德的生活，请在我们的村里走一走，和大家谈一谈吧。<<A<<[CHANGED 2020/07/08]
message.zh_TW: 感謝你為我們村莊帶來了和平。<<A<<[CHANGED 2020/07/09]
message.ja_JP:
\v[lore.title.seeker]さん、シャッドの村を
歩いて、今もマシンを我らのものと
したいか聞いてみてくだされ。<<A<<[CHANGED 2020/07/03]
message.ko_KR: \v[lore.title.seeker], 기계를 들일 방법을 찾고 싶다면 샤드 마을 돌아다니며 주민들에게 말을 걸어봐라.<<A<<[CHANGED 2020/07/08]

message.en_US: Human machines bring prosperity and coolness to shad village.\. And they working with clean power.
message.pt_BR: As máquinas humanas trouxeram prosperidade e frescor à aldeia dos shad.\. E elas trabalham com energia limpa.
message.de_DE: Menschmaschine bringen Wohlstand und Kühle in Shaddorf.\. Und arbeiten mit sauber Energie.
message.zh_CN: 人类机器为沙德村庄带来了繁荣和凉爽。\.而且使用的是清洁能源。<<A<<[CHANGED 2020/07/08]
message.zh_TW: 感謝你為我們村莊帶來了和平。<<A<<[CHANGED 2020/07/09]
message.ja_JP:
人間のマシン、シャッドの村に
繁栄と涼しさを持ってきてくれる。
\.そしてクリーンなパワーで動く。<<A<<[CHANGED 2020/07/03]
message.ko_KR: 인간 기계 샤드 마을에 번영과 시원함을 준다.\. 게다가 깨끗한 전력으로 구동되지.<<A<<[CHANGED 2020/07/08]

message.en_US: \v[lore.title.seeker], this is worldly blessing in harmony with the track and shad traditions.\. You have our thanks.
message.pt_BR: \v[lore.title.seeker], isto é uma bênção universal em harmonia com as tradições da trilha e dos shad.\. Você tem a nossa gratidão.
message.de_DE: Seeker, dies sein weltlicher Segen im Einklang mit Pfad- und Shad-Tradition.\. Wir dir sehr danken.<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/05/22]
message.zh_CN: \v[lore.title.seeker]，这不仅是与自然和谐共处，也符合沙德传统。\.谢谢你。<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/05/22]
message.zh_TW: 感謝你為我們村莊帶來了和平。<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/05/22]
message.ja_JP:
\v[lore.title.seeker]さん、これは軌跡と
シャッドの伝統が相まった、
この世のお恵みですな。
\.感謝いたします。<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/05/22]
message.ko_KR: \v[lore.title.seeker], 이것은 고대인의 길과 샤드의 전통이 조화를 이루는 축복이다.\. 고맙군.<<A<<[CHANGED 2020/07/08]

message.en_US: Hello Seeker! It's good to see you.
message.pt_BR: Olá Seeker! É bom ver você.
message.de_DE: Hallo, Seeker! Schön, dich zu sehen.
message.zh_CN: 你好啊探索者！见到你很高兴。<<A<<[CHANGED 2017/12/12]
message.ja_JP:
こんにちは、探索者さん！
お会いできてよかった。<<A<<[CHANGED 2017/11/27]
message.zh_TW: 你好啊探索者！見到你很高興。<<A<<[CHANGED 2017/12/12]

message.en_US: No more Wiccats have infested the village.
message.pt_BR: Os Wiccats não infestaram mais a aldeia.
message.de_DE: Das Dorf ist weiterhin frei von Schnurrken.
message.zh_CN: 邪猫没有再来骚扰村子了。<<A<<[CHANGED 2017/12/12]
message.ja_JP:
村を侵食していた
ウィキャットはもういません。<<A<<[CHANGED 2017/11/27]
message.zh_TW: 邪貓沒有再來騷擾村子了。<<A<<[CHANGED 2017/12/12]

message.en_US: And the Shad have calmed down.
message.pt_BR: E os Shad se acalmaram.
message.de_DE: Und die Shad haben sich beruhigt.
message.zh_CN: 沙德人也平息了下来。<<A<<[CHANGED 2017/12/12]
message.ja_JP: シャッドたちも落ち着きました。<<A<<[CHANGED 2017/11/27]
message.zh_TW: 沙德人也平息了下來。<<A<<[CHANGED 2017/12/12]

message.en_US: Hello Seeker! It's good to see you.
message.pt_BR: Olá Seeker! É bom ver você.
message.de_DE: Hallo, Seeker! Schön, dich zu sehen.
message.zh_CN: 探索者你好！见到你很高兴。<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/08/28]
message.ja_JP:
こんにちは、探索者さん！
お会いできてよかった。<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/08/28]
message.zh_TW: 探索者你好！見到你很高興。<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/08/28]

message.en_US: Thanks so much for finding the source of this vile infestation!
message.pt_BR: Muito obrigada por encontrar a fonte dessa infestação terrível!
message.de_DE: Vielen Dank, dass du die Quelle dieser fürchterlichen Seuche ausgeschaltet hast!
message.zh_CN: 多谢你找到了感染源！<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/10/04]
message.ja_JP:
村を侵食していた
ウィキャットは見つけてくれてありがとう！<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/10/04]
message.ko_KR: 이 끔찍한 습격의 근원을 찾아줘서 정말 고마워!<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/10/04]
message.zh_TW: 多謝你找到了感染源！<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/10/04]
